## n8n@0.73.0 For a comprehensive list of changes, check out the [commits](https://github.com/n8n-io/n8n/compare/n8n@0.72.0...n8n@0.73.0) for this version.
**Release date:** 2020-07-08 - New nodes - CircleCI - Microsoft SQL - Zoom - Enhanced nodes - Postmark Trigger - Salesforce - It's now possible to set default values for credentials that get prefilled, and the user can't change.
